{"tid":1748460,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[Good News] 梁天琦在重審中脫罪，毋需加監！！！","createTime":"2019-11-23T16:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T17:41:26.000Z","uid":134093,"like":39,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4289d921debacb3632042f6b2f19fc204bfdf5a9","tid":1748460,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:35:18.000Z","msg":"一年多經歷兩次審訊的梁天琦，去年因暴動和襲警罪被判囚6年。<br />\n惟該案陪審團未能就其中1罪達成大比數裁決，該罪需重審，並和「美國隊長」容偉業涉暴動案合併。<br />\n梁在是次重審脫罪，毋需加監。而梁天琦的律師透露，梁預計於2022年1月19日出獄，同時他已就原審的定罪提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SCX2O7O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSCX2O7O.jpg&h=91be58a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bf335663b2bbe90127a12953dae20748a1b7a2f","tid":1748460,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fa79343bd06e1832b0b783a8178311132d2c14","tid":1748460,"uid":134093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d426ec50279d32db29b18bcb3db204130929fe3","tid":1748460,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"唔明 即刻點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a199303ed59094e863de7cc569306cc34ed16924","tid":1748460,"uid":288537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:37:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f55dd234a2045e1e63e286aa4f51a35657ae71bd","tid":1748460,"uid":134093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"2022年or less"},{"pid":"a974793a3803a640354b45b40592443cf79cee81","tid":1748460,"uid":288537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:37:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45c12b423a31e7e08afe6f54b3526b5670ea2533","tid":1